{"tid":182511,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 印度咖喱雞","createTime":"2017-04-01T11:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T22:51:41.000Z","uid":74981,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59e1ce5c661c9151393f4fa115678a6ac2a44761","tid":182511,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"印度咖喱雞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/4d86de79d6540e4525df885628403a60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F4d86de79d6540e4525df885628403a60.jpg&h=e3949b94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片如下:<br />\n<br />\nPART 1<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/et7dslv1I4U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fet7dslv1I4U&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=757218b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/et7dslv1I4U</a><br />\n<br />\nPART2<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LsVLZ-ILTeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLsVLZ-ILTeg&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=dfa55fc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LsVLZ-ILTeg</a><br />\n<br />\n材料:<br />\n<br />\n雞1.5隻 (要斬大舊D)<br />\n紫洋蔥3個<br />\n本地蓄茄8個<br />\n小馬鈴薯10個<br />\n蒜頭大半個打蓉<br />\n薑數小粒打蓉<br />\n<br />\n香料A (用來爆)<br />\n芫茜子粒2茶匙<br />\n黑胡椒粒1茶匙<br />\n青砂仁4粒<br />\n桂皮1小片<br />\n月桂葉2片<br />\n丁香6粒<br />\n<br />\n香料B (磨粉)<br />\n孜然粒1湯匙 (磨粉)<br />\n芫茜子1湯匙 (磨粉)<br />\n黑胡椒粒2茶匙 (磨粉)<br />\n青砂仁4粒 (磨粉)<br />\n草果1粒 (磨粉)<br />\n桂皮3小片 (磨粉)<br />\n<br />\n香料C (就咁落)<br />\n黃薑粉1湯匙<br />\n辣椒粉1湯匙<br />\n月桂葉2片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香料D (遲D落)<br />\n青辣椒2隻打蓉<br />\n<br />\n做法:<br />\n<br />\n1. 獲燒紅, 熄火落油轉中火, 爆香雞件, 大慨2成熟.<br />\n<br />\n2. 隔油撈起雞, 用番D油爆洋蔥同香料A<br />\n<br />\n3. 洋蔥炒至金黃色, 唔好俾佢燶, 然後落薑蒜蓉炒香, 再落蕃茄粒炒, 然後落少少水&quot;COME&quot;獲蓋煮10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n4. 其間, 間中開獲蓋用獲剷剷下個底等佢唔好痴底<br />\n<br />\n5. 開獲蓋, 落香料B同C, 略炒, 落兩碗半水, 開大火煮滖, &quot;COME&quot;獲蓋, 收細火煮60分鐘, 其間不時要打開獲蓋, 剷下個底, 確保唔會痴底, 如果見乾得濟, 打開獲蓋, 加大半碗水, 開大火煮滖, &quot;COME&quot;獲蓋, 收細火煮, 哩個步驟要重覆幾次<br />\n<br />\n6. 60分鐘後, 落馬鈴薯, 大火煮滖, &quot;COME&quot;獲蓋, 收細火煮45分鐘, 其間不時要打開獲蓋, 剷下個底, 確保唔會痴底, 如果見乾得濟, 打開獲蓋, 加大半碗水, 開大火煮滖, &quot;COME&quot;獲蓋, 收細火煮, 哩個步驟要重覆幾次<br />\n<br />\n7. 45分鐘後, 落雞同香料D, 大火煮滖, &quot;COME&quot;獲蓋, 收細火煮15分鐘, 熄火, 浸2個鐘<br />\n<br />\n8. 完成. 雞好滑, 唔會煮到老, 又入哂咖喱味, 好食到.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c5ec923933d3b436853580c6cd99fa5ebf2e76","tid":182511,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4594e3ecd557162746b2563f141684bf5e8e05","tid":182511,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920c03933bcc65c1a93c7b71c545c4d3d39bbf87","tid":182511,"uid":41689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"我都係用呢個牌子洗衣機喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd09101ff72e8cd82d6e86233539cebcb47b177","tid":182511,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b68b3246dc85517d156fcd5864ae3e4585c437","tid":182511,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n